135
00:05:33.441 --> 00:05:35.287
at different frequencies

136
00:05:35.287 --> 00:05:39.850
thus driving the brain into a state of automatic relaxation,

137
00:05:39.850 --> 00:05:42.961
and as a last minute throw in

138
00:05:42.961 --> 00:05:45.922
there was a guided imagery tape that I had produced

139
00:05:45.922 --> 00:05:50.922
that used imagining good outcomes as the way to go.

