00:31:09.079 --> 00:31:11.459
insanely swinging neuro hormones

733
00:31:11.459 --> 00:31:13.189
that are going back and forth

734
00:31:13.189 --> 00:31:17.264
and one side of the pendulum is intense,

735
00:31:17.264 --> 00:31:22.264
adrenergized, activated emotions

