00:31:47.356 --> 00:31:49.862
which is the body's way of trying to mediate

744
00:31:49.862 --> 00:31:52.636
these crazy adrenaline symptoms.

745
00:31:52.636 --> 00:31:55.237
So you're kind of gorked out,

746
00:31:55.237 --> 00:31:59.777
you look stoned, your concentration is bad,

