1075
00:46:29.178 --> 00:46:32.348
We're taking functional MRIs of their brains

1076
00:46:32.348 --> 00:46:35.285
before this and after.

1077
00:46:35.285 --> 00:46:37.154
We expect to see differences.

1078
00:46:37.154 --> 00:46:41.647
And we're taking a very complicated

1079
00:46:41.647 --> 00:46:45.664
